Package: SmoothExport
Title: Creating smart flextable objects from R dataframes
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2019-06-18
Authors@R: person("Artem", "Zefirov", email = "zefirovart@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides the tools for R dataframes conversion into flextable objects, the design of which can be adjusted flexibly. Generated objects with appropriate captions can be exported into Word files yeilding the ready-made part of any official report.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
Imports:
	stats (>= 3.4.0),
	magrittr (>= 1.5),
	tibble (>= 2.0.1),
	dplyr (>= 0.7.8),
	flextable (>= 0.4.6),
	officer (>= 0.3.2)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Suggests: 
    testthat
